{"title":"通过媒体介质创建工具重装","time":"2022 年 6 月 27 日","shareable":true,"id":"guide/tip/win/media-reinstall","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"p","type":"tip","heading":"我该选择 Windows 10 还是 Windows 11?","text":["Windows 11 是微软的最新操作系统版本，它也具有更加美观的页面。如果您的笔记本是在 18 年之后销售或生产的，那么它大概率 (> 95%) 符合 Windows 11 的安装要求。","由于 Windows 10 和 Windows 11 内核相差很小，切换到 Windows 11 并不会出现兼容性问题，所以如果您的设备支持 Windows 11，Mr.Hope 推荐您在重装时切换到 Windows 11。请点击查看如何确定您的电脑是否支持 Windows 11。"],"path":"guide/tip/win/win11/support"},{"tag":"title","text":"启动盘制作"},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"Windows 11 启动盘制作","icon":"udisk","path":"guide/tip/win/win11/media"},{"text":"Windows 10 启动盘制作","icon":"udisk","path":"guide/tip/win/win10/media"}]},{"tag":"title","text":"从启动盘启动"},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"从启动盘启动","icon":"play","path":"guide/tip/win/usb-boot"}]},{"tag":"title","text":"系统安装"},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"Windows 11 安装","icon":"idea","path":"guide/tip/win/win11/install"},{"text":"Windows 10 安装","icon":"idea","path":"guide/tip/win/win10/install"}]},{"tag":"title","text":"用户设置向导"},{"tag":"text","text":["通常情况下，这一步骤您可自行按照指引完成，不过 Mr.Hope 还是截屏了完整步骤以防您需要。"]},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"Windows 11 用户向导","icon":"intro","path":"guide/tip/win/win11/setup"},{"text":"Windows 10 用户向导","icon":"intro","path":"guide/tip/win/win10/setup"}]}]}